      "notes": [
        "Design language: dark, premium, glassy surfaces with soft elevation and a single violet accent.",
        "Avoid hard borders and harsh contrast; rely on blur, subtle gradients, and gentle shadows."
      ]
    },
    "intendedUse": "High-level design system guidelines for an AI/code generator to replicate this look across web + native UI. When implementing components, reference the tamagui.config.ts and theme files listed in implementationNotes.tamagui for actual token values and implementation details."
